# Implementation Plan - Google Tag Manager (GTM) Migration and Custom Event Tracking

Migrate the application from Google Analytics to Google Tag Manager (GTM) using the `@next/third-parties/google` package. We will implement global custom event tracking (contextual telemetry via `journey_string` path and first-party user data for Enhanced Conversions).

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Root Layout

