### 3. B. Form Events

We will track successful form submissions (excluding invalid/incomplete attempts) and pass Enhanced Conversions fields (`user_email`, `user_phone`, `user_name`).

#### [MODIFY] [HeroQuoteForm.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/forms/HeroQuoteForm.tsx)
- Accept `placement` as a prop (defaults to `"hero_form"` / `"lp_hero_form"` dynamically using `usePathname`).
- Import `usePathname` from `next/navigation` and `sendGTMEvent` from `@next/third-parties/google`.
- On successful validation and submission (`response.success`), fire `submit_partial_lead` with the schema:
  - `placement`: prop/computed value
  - `journey_string`: current pathname
  - `services_requested`: array of selected service IDs
  - `user_data`: `{ user_email, user_phone }`

#### [MODIFY] [QuoteDialog.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/QuoteDialog.tsx)
- Accept an optional `placement` prop and forward it to `HeroQuoteForm`.

#### [MODIFY] [DynamicQuoteForm.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/forms/quote/DynamicQuoteForm.tsx)
- Import `usePathname` from `next/navigation` and `sendGTMEvent` from `@next/third-parties/google`.
- Accept an optional `placement` prop (defaults to `"booking_form"`).
- On successful server validation and submission (`res.success`), fire `submit_final_booking` with the schema:
  - `placement`: prop/computed value
  - `journey_string`: current pathname
  - `value`: minimum estimated price (from `priceRange.min`)
  - `currency`: `'AUD'`
  - `user_data`: `{ user_email, user_phone, user_name }`

